        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: '...They should be able to get this place up and running like before in no time. But anyway, I never thought the reinforcements from Babylonia would be 【kuroname】 and you, Rosetta.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
