        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I\\'m only temporarily staying at Babylonia. So if the ARU requires help, I\\'d naturally be the most appropriate candidate.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'What about you, 【kuroname】?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 1012,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'At the behest of our dear Rosetta.', 3: '17', 4: 'Thanks for your help in Kowloong.', 5: '19'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": 18,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Huh, I see... So Constructs in Babylonia get to appoint their commandants? If 【kuroname】 is on the menu, then color me intrigued.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": 23,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'This is only a temporary arrangement. 【kuroname】 is still the commandant for the Gray Ravens.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": 20,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Oh... You found out? And here I was, hoping to be a hero behind the scenes.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": 21,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Don\\'t try something that dangerous again, Diana. Especially with my kind of luck.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": 22,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Sigh, here you go with the luck stuff again, Rosetta.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": 23,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: '...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Anyway, 【kuroname】... Did Rosetta make you wear this?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 1013,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'A big plump robot I am...', 3: '24', 4: 'Yes.', 5: '25'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": 26,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'It\\'s bulky, but it has the defensive capability to match. And if you activate its built-in acceleration system, you might just be able to keep up with us for a few seconds.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": 26,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'That means she cares about you.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'These Polar Soldier units just feel so nice and smooth. I\\'ve seen all sorts of piloted models, but somehow this one gives me warm and fuzzy feelings inside...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'From gentle head-scritches of your Polar Soldier unit, Diana\\'s hand gradually quickens into rambunctious rubbing. The paint above your head is definitely thinning.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Diana... Now\\'s not the time for that. Do you have info on the current situation?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Of course. We saw the Babylonia reinforcements leaving the stronghold, and rushed over. Now we can recover the lost territory.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 1014,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'You should be able to handle the bionics.', 3: '30', 4: 'What were you guys doing before?', 5: '33'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": 31,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'True, but we\\'re shorthanded. If we want to hold a region, we\\'ll have to station too many of our forces.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": 32,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'And if we don\\'t do so, no matter how many areas we recover, they\\'ll likely be recaptured again.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": 1015,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'That\\'s why we were engaging in guerrilla warfare up until this point.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": 1015,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'We were conducting guerrilla warfare. The enemy has us outnumbered, so we have to resort to picking off the enemies trying to attack the main base.', 4: '1'}"
